  "questions": [
    {
      "text": "A 25-year-old woman presents with six weeks of frequent vomiting, muscle weakness, and fatigue. She denies laxative use and reports no abdominal pain. Examination reveals dry mucous membranes (see lab results and report).\n\n\nHeart rate\n105/min\n\n\nBlood pressure\n92/64 mm Hg\n\n\n\n\nTest\nResult\nNormal Values\n\n\n\nPotassium\n2.7 mmol/L\n3.5 - 5.1 mmol/L\n\n\nBicarbonate\n36 mmol/L\n21 - 28 mmol/L\n\n\nArterial blood gas\n\n\n\n\n pH\n7.48\n7.36 - 7.45\n\n\n\nElectrocardiogram: T-wave flattening\nWhich of the following interventions is most appropriate?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Intravenous normal saline with potassium supplementation"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Intravenous sodium bicarbonate infusion"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Immediate endoscopic evaluation"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Intravenous magnesium replacement"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 1,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) CORRECT:</h4>This patient presents with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=zL0rZS&anker=Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"zL0rZS\" data-anker=\"Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-section-id=\"sRctoX0\" data-sememe-id=\"thaXf4\">metabolic alkalosis</a>, characterized by elevated <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=M60MlS&anker=Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-learningcard-id=\"M60MlS\" data-anker=\"Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-section-id=\"O8cI5V0\" data-sememe-id=\"JmXsgA\">bicarbonate</a> and alkalotic <span data-sememe-id=\"Kr1URR0\">pH</span>, due to frequent <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7J04vS&anker=Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\">vomiting</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7J04vS&anker=Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\">Vomiting</a> leads to loss of gastric <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=M60MlS&anker=Z2b222329949064378f320c11017a71ee\" data-learningcard-id=\"M60MlS\" data-anker=\"Z2b222329949064378f320c11017a71ee\" data-section-id=\"O8cI5V0\" data-sememe-id=\"pmXLgA\">hydrochloric acid</a>, resulting in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z9806729817abdbcbf37c8237327ccabf\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z9806729817abdbcbf37c8237327ccabf\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"Z5YZip\">chloride</a> and hydrogen ion depletion. This, along with <span data-sememe-id=\"7tc4UV0\">volume depletion</span>, causes renal retention of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=M60MlS&anker=Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-learningcard-id=\"M60MlS\" data-anker=\"Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-section-id=\"O8cI5V0\" data-sememe-id=\"JmXsgA\">bicarbonate</a>. Intravenous <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=fM0kLg&anker=Zca7fd28598a951a5b85443bbe965acd0\" data-learningcard-id=\"fM0kLg\" data-anker=\"Zca7fd28598a951a5b85443bbe965acd0\" data-section-id=\"kdcmJY0\" data-sememe-id=\"wWbhns\">normal saline</a> restores <span data-sememe-id=\"9FYN4I\">intravascular</span> volume and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z9806729817abdbcbf37c8237327ccabf\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z9806729817abdbcbf37c8237327ccabf\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"Z5YZip\">chloride</a>, aiding in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=M60MlS&anker=Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-learningcard-id=\"M60MlS\" data-anker=\"Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-section-id=\"O8cI5V0\" data-sememe-id=\"JmXsgA\">bicarbonate</a> excretion. <span data-sememe-id=\"brWHf50\">Potassium</span> supplementation is crucial, as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=lI0v1h&anker=Z1454fccf44cdd1776601d443f63ca03c\" data-learningcard-id=\"lI0v1h\" data-anker=\"Z1454fccf44cdd1776601d443f63ca03c\" data-sememe-id=\"gG0FAh\">hypokalemia</a> can exacerbate <span data-sememe-id=\"T7b6OE\">alkalosis</span> by promoting intracellular <span data-sememe-id=\"brWHf50\">potassium</span> shifts and extracellular hydrogen ion shifts. This approach addresses the fluid and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"-mYDRp\">electrolyte</a> imbalances associated with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7J04vS&anker=Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\">vomiting</a>-induced <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=zL0rZS&anker=Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"zL0rZS\" data-anker=\"Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-section-id=\"sRctoX0\" data-sememe-id=\"thaXf4\">metabolic alkalosis</a>.<br><br><span class=\"wichtig\"><b>Key learning point: </b></span>Frequent <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7J04vS&anker=Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\">vomiting</a> leads to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=zL0rZS&anker=Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"zL0rZS\" data-anker=\"Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-section-id=\"sRctoX0\" data-sememe-id=\"thaXf4\">metabolic alkalosis</a> due to the loss of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=M60MlS&anker=Z2b222329949064378f320c11017a71ee\" data-learningcard-id=\"M60MlS\" data-anker=\"Z2b222329949064378f320c11017a71ee\" data-section-id=\"O8cI5V0\" data-sememe-id=\"pmXLgA\">gastric acid</a>, and is often associated with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=lI0v1h&anker=Z1454fccf44cdd1776601d443f63ca03c\" data-learningcard-id=\"lI0v1h\" data-anker=\"Z1454fccf44cdd1776601d443f63ca03c\" data-sememe-id=\"gG0FAh\">hypokalemia</a>, as indicated by <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pl0LBT&anker=Zf57bff8d5455c72457da0440f636f4bc\" data-learningcard-id=\"pl0LBT\" data-anker=\"Zf57bff8d5455c72457da0440f636f4bc\" data-sememe-id=\"jn0_Gg\">ECG</a> changes such as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=pl0LBT&anker=Z06d1b22dd1fb2c6da671550b3b22584b\" data-learningcard-id=\"pl0LBT\" data-anker=\"Z06d1b22dd1fb2c6da671550b3b22584b\" data-section-id=\"rNcfc10\" data-sememe-id=\"lO1vsS0\">T-wave flattening</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span data-sememe-id=\"hCbc7D\">Sodium bicarbonate</span> infusion is used for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=zL0rZS&anker=Ze6ecd1a689f21c50f6f1d77dcd2bd10b\" data-learningcard-id=\"zL0rZS\" data-anker=\"Ze6ecd1a689f21c50f6f1d77dcd2bd10b\" data-section-id=\"sRctoX0\" data-sememe-id=\"GhaB24\">metabolic acidosis</a> with low <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=M60MlS&anker=Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-learningcard-id=\"M60MlS\" data-anker=\"Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-section-id=\"O8cI5V0\" data-sememe-id=\"JmXsgA\">bicarbonate</a> and <span data-sememe-id=\"Kr1URR0\">pH</span>. This patient has elevated <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=M60MlS&anker=Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-learningcard-id=\"M60MlS\" data-anker=\"Z6cdbbc46116e490c8de4fb6acf44242c\" data-section-id=\"O8cI5V0\" data-sememe-id=\"JmXsgA\">bicarbonate</a> and alkalotic <span data-sememe-id=\"Kr1URR0\">pH</span>, indicating <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=zL0rZS&anker=Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"zL0rZS\" data-anker=\"Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-section-id=\"sRctoX0\" data-sememe-id=\"thaXf4\">metabolic alkalosis</a> from <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7J04vS&anker=Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\">vomiting</a>. <span data-sememe-id=\"hCbc7D\">Sodium bicarbonate</span> would worsen <span data-sememe-id=\"T7b6OE\">alkalosis</span> and does not address volume contraction or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"-mYDRp\">electrolyte</a> imbalances.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>Endoscopy is indicated for suspected <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ZS0Zy2&anker=Z63797faee8c413c0c066ee4e1af342dc\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZS0Zy2\" data-anker=\"Z63797faee8c413c0c066ee4e1af342dc\" data-section-id=\"uJ1pD30\" data-sememe-id=\"hF0c33\">upper gastrointestinal bleeding</a> or structural lesions, not for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=zL0rZS&anker=Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"zL0rZS\" data-anker=\"Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-section-id=\"sRctoX0\" data-sememe-id=\"thaXf4\">metabolic alkalosis</a> due to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7J04vS&anker=Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\">vomiting</a>. This patient lacks signs of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ZS0Zy2&anker=Z5b38a059d860d4f7f79d2947306c643e\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZS0Zy2\" data-anker=\"Z5b38a059d860d4f7f79d2947306c643e\" data-sememe-id=\"M40MPT\">gastrointestinal bleeding</a> or structural pathology, making endoscopy unnecessary. The focus should be on correcting fluid and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z562f1491861b33bdb5af572388e99541\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"-mYDRp\">electrolyte</a> imbalances.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=QJ0uFS&anker=Z107660be27ffff5053cf62439d061538\" data-learningcard-id=\"QJ0uFS\" data-anker=\"Z107660be27ffff5053cf62439d061538\" data-section-id=\"fZ1ka20\">Magnesium replacement</a> is indicated for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=sq0t-S&anker=Zd4e2194d3ccbce7ba40364b7d381b6cd\" data-learningcard-id=\"sq0t-S\" data-anker=\"Zd4e2194d3ccbce7ba40364b7d381b6cd\" data-sememe-id=\"umbph8\">hypomagnesemia</a> or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7S04af&anker=Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"7S04af\" data-anker=\"Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-sememe-id=\"Yk0nmT\">arrhythmias</a> due to low <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z48646e3ac5ed3ef7bb2a82b1b72e4186\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z48646e3ac5ed3ef7bb2a82b1b72e4186\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"05Yeip\">magnesium</a>. This patient has no evidence of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ln0wFg&anker=Z48646e3ac5ed3ef7bb2a82b1b72e4186\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ln0wFg\" data-anker=\"Z48646e3ac5ed3ef7bb2a82b1b72e4186\" data-section-id=\"Bacz5a0\" data-sememe-id=\"05Yeip\">magnesium</a> deficiency or related <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7S04af&anker=Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"7S04af\" data-anker=\"Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-sememe-id=\"Yk0nmT\">arrhythmias</a>. The primary issue is <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7J04vS&anker=Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\" data-learningcard-id=\"7J04vS\" data-anker=\"Z2f0b48ef2acaab783b03e4c8d2404f90\">vomiting</a>-induced <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=zL0rZS&anker=Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-learningcard-id=\"zL0rZS\" data-anker=\"Z46196a0a09cd3ccdd01835db5b427a7c\" data-section-id=\"sRctoX0\" data-sememe-id=\"thaXf4\">metabolic alkalosis</a>, best addressed with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=kO0msT&anker=Zee3c52d5a0e0844921b94c537f7d8ba3\" data-learningcard-id=\"kO0msT\" data-anker=\"Zee3c52d5a0e0844921b94c537f7d8ba3\" data-section-id=\"6r1jRR0\" data-sememe-id=\"NgY-vo\">fluid resuscitation</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=QJ0uFS&anker=Z6ceab98716fa4c42f9a213856674416c\" data-learningcard-id=\"QJ0uFS\" data-anker=\"Z6ceab98716fa4c42f9a213856674416c\" data-section-id=\"oV10vf0\">potassium replacement</a>.</div>",
